484
00:19:34,758 --> 00:19:37,802
But then, one day,
I was in the back office,

485
00:19:37,886 --> 00:19:39,804
and I was going through
some books,

486
00:19:39,846 --> 00:19:43,266
and the recipe just, sort of...

