488
00:19:45,393 --> 00:19:46,978
Do you think
he'd been hiding it?

489
00:19:47,020 --> 00:19:49,564
Maybe.

490
00:19:49,606 --> 00:19:52,484
It certainly felt like...

491
00:19:52,567 --> 00:19:55,278
